very nice to you.

619
00:31:28,720 --> 00:31:29,520
No way.

620
00:31:31,720 --> 00:31:32,560
The more she pushes me away,

621
00:31:32,960 --> 00:31:34,120
the more I have to

622
00:31:34,120 --> 00:31:35,160
show my face in front of her.

623
00:31:35,600 --> 00:31:37,280
I will prove with my actions

624
00:31:37,600 --> 00:31:38,720
that I will cherish
her precious daughter

625
00:31:39,200 --> 00:31:40,640
