629
00:31:50,400 --> 00:31:51,480
You again?

630
00:31:51,960 --> 00:31:53,200
I got you breakfast.

631
00:31:57,000 --> 00:31:57,800
Auntie.

632
00:32:01,520 --> 00:32:03,000
This fish is tasty. It's good!

633
00:32:11,920 --> 00:32:13,080
Auntie!

634
00:32:16,200 --> 00:32:17,600
