639
00:32:44,080 --> 00:32:45,000
Give up.

640
00:32:45,160 --> 00:32:45,640
No, Auntie.

641
00:32:47,920 --> 00:32:48,600
If you say that,

642
00:32:48,600 --> 00:32:50,520
