find any flaws with you.

649
00:33:05,120 --> 00:33:05,960
But

650
00:33:07,160 --> 00:33:08,840
your dad sees my Wei'an

651
00:33:08,840 --> 00:33:10,160
with discrimination.

652
00:33:10,600 --> 00:33:11,640
Do you know,

653
00:33:11,920 --> 00:33:12,720
to me, Wei'an

654
00:33:12,720 --> 00:33:14,880
is the most important person
in this world?

655
00:33:15,080 --> 00:33:16,280
So I cannot

656
00:33:16,280 --> 00:33:18,360
Allow anyone to belittle her.

657
00:33:20,480 --> 00:33:22,080
Don't waste your time here

658
00:33:22,080 --> 00:33:23,080
or your efforts.

659
00:33:23,920 --> 00:33:24,680
Auntie!

660
00:33:37,360 --> 00:33:38,160
Dr. Gu,

661
00:33:39,480 --> 00:33:40,720
