662
00:33:43,360 --> 00:33:44,400
It's great.

663
00:33:44,960 --> 00:33:46,520
I got a lot of it these days.

664
00:33:47,240 --> 00:33:49,080
Weren't you always treasuring time?

665
00:33:49,600 --> 00:33:50,560
How come you're spending

666
00:33:50,560 --> 00:33:52,000
so much time on Lan?

667
00:33:53,080 --> 00:33:54,600
I have to make my mother-in-law like me.

668
00:33:55,080 --> 00:33:56,200
In that case,

669
00:33:56,640 --> 00:33:58,680
I can have a good girlfriend like you.

670
00:34:00,640 --> 00:34:02,640
You're so gentle and considerate in life

671
00:34:02,960 --> 00:34:04,480
and can work over

672
00:34:04,840 --> 00:34:06,480
12 hours a day for me.

673
00:34:06,920 --> 00:34:08,280
