674
00:34:08,840 --> 00:34:10,080
You old cunning fox.

675
00:34:11,080 --> 00:34:11,670
What?

676
00:34:11,960 --> 00:34:12,600
Old?

677
00:34:13,670 --> 00:34:14,670
Aren't you?

678
00:34:15,320 --> 00:34:16,670
You're six years older than me.

679
00:34:17,920 --> 00:34:18,880
