682
00:34:36,080 --> 00:34:36,920
Yes.

683
00:34:38,040 --> 00:34:39,230
Su Wei'an, don't run!

684
00:34:49,880 --> 00:34:51,320
Being your girlfriend is too tiring.

685
00:34:51,710 --> 00:34:53,080
Overuse of mental faculties
during work hours

686
00:34:53,080 --> 00:34:54,400
