705
00:35:52,080 --> 00:35:53,720
I added a lot of osmanthus!

706
00:35:53,720 --> 00:35:55,320
Open up and try it!

707
00:36:00,840 --> 00:36:01,560
Auntie.

708
00:36:02,280 --> 00:36:03,200
What are you doing here?

709
00:36:03,720 --> 00:36:04,920
I've told you

710
00:36:04,920 --> 00:36:07,040
that acting like a stalker won't work!

711
00:36:08,000 --> 00:36:09,240
He's here to help.

712
00:36:10,960 --> 00:36:12,200
What kind of help?

713
00:36:16,920 --> 00:36:17,720
Auntie Su,

714
00:36:17,960 --> 00:36:18,680
look,

715
00:36:19,400 --> 00:36:21,040
the weather is really nice today!

716
00:36:22,720 --> 00:36:24,280
In our small courtyard upstairs,

717
00:36:24,480 --> 00:36:25,560
the flowers have all bloomed.

718
00:36:25,560 --> 00:36:26,920
I brought you here to take a look.

719
00:36:28,040 --> 00:36:28,720
You can't

720
00:36:28,720 --> 00:36:30,480
only stay in your room every day.

721
00:36:30,480 --> 00:36:32,880
You should come out and get some sun.

722
00:36:35,520 --> 00:36:37,560
Look, the flowers over there,

723
00:36:38,560 --> 00:36:39,440
aren't they so pretty?

724
00:38:42,760 --> 00:38:43,560
Let's go back.

725
00:38:44,720 --> 00:38:45,760
Mrs. Su!

726
00:38:47,920 --> 00:38:48,640
Mrs. Su!

727
00:38:48,640 --> 00:38:50,040
We all miss you a lot.

728
00:38:50,280 --> 00:38:51,080
Mrs. Su.

729
00:38:53,040 --> 00:38:54,360
I miss you too.

730
00:38:58,720 --> 00:38:59,520
Mom,

731
00:39:00,760 --> 00:39:01,800
it was Gu Yunzheng who contacted

732
00:39:02,160 --> 00:39:04,240
Auntie's former colleagues
from the orchestra,

733
00:39:04,760 --> 00:39:06,200
hoping they could come
to keep Auntie company.

734
00:39:06,440 --> 00:39:07,240
Yunzheng,

735
00:39:08,080 --> 00:39:09,160
thank you.

736
00:39:09,200 --> 00:39:10,000
Auntie,

737
00:39:10,720 --> 00:39:12,360
