779
00:41:20,720 --> 00:41:22,760
I know. I mean,

780
00:41:23,160 --> 00:41:25,680
before Microlight Fund grants
our application,

781
00:41:25,920 --> 00:41:26,720
use my money.

782
00:41:26,720 --> 00:41:27,880
Microlight Fund?

783
00:41:27,880 --> 00:41:28,520
Yes.

784
00:41:28,840 --> 00:41:29,920
Microlight Fund

